### [성공] 관리자 로그인 | 기대: 200 | 핵심 확인: accessToken, refreshToken 갱신
POST {{authHost}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeEmail": "hyunsu.kim@seto.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}

### [성공] 토큰 갱신 | 기대: 200 | 핵심 확인: accessToken 재발급
POST {{authHost}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Cookie: refreshToken={{refreshToken}}

> {%
    client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
    client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}

### [성공] 로그아웃 | 기대: 200
POST {{authHost}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Cookie: refreshToken={{refreshToken}}
